# 7. ステージにかける想い

Minori: I hope you'll listen!
Yuina: Minori...
Minori: I... I, umm...
Haruka: M-Minori...
Airi: Tongue-tied right out of the gates. That sure is a unique talent.
Yuina: You can do it, Minori...!
Minori: U-Uhh... I.. I...!
Minori: I've been looking up to a certain idol ever since I was little... I've always wanted to be an idol just like her...!
Minori: But things really didn't go all that well... I failed pretty much every audition I applied for...
Minori: So, being able to stand here today... I still can't believe this is really happening right now.
Haruka: Minori...
Minori: U-Uhh... Everyone who's been following MORE MORE JUMP! since we first formed might already know this...
Minori: But I had so much trouble doing anything in the beginning. I felt awful because I thought that I was holding the others back...
Yuina: N-No, that's not true! We know you were doing your best, Minori!
Fans: Yeah!
Minori: Oh... Hehe. Thanks!
Minori: However, as concerned as I was, I didn't want to give up on my dream. Not only that...
Minori: I really love MORE MORE JUMP! That's why I decided to do everything I could to make sure we could spread hope to all of you.
Minori: But I... I had a realization as we kept doing stuff together.
Minori: Idols don't just give hope to others! We're also in a position to receive hope!
Hasegawa: Receive hope...?
Minori: And everyone in MORE MORE JUMP! has given me so much! They taught me everything about being an idol... From how to carry myself emotionally to all the techniques I need to know...
Minori: Oh, and Airi taught me so much leading up to today's performance!
Minori: And everyone in SEKAI... No, wait! I meant all the other idols who've helped me along the way!
Minori: They helped me as I practiced my dancing, gave me advice when I had something on my mind... And I can't thank them enough for it!
Luka: <Oh, is she talking about us...?>
Miku: <Wow, that's so sweet of her...>
Minori: I need to thank our invited guests for their contributions as well. We're standing here today because you were there for us when we really needed your help!
Minori: All of these people around us have given our group so much... More than I can recall... We appreciate each and every one of you for what you've done.
Minori: But above all else... The ones I need to thank the most are...
Minori: All of you! The fans!
Yuina: ...!
Minori: We're a little different from the idols you're all probably used to seeing... But we've been able to put on events and other fun activities because of your help!
Minori: Oh, also! These adorable outfits that Shizuku designed! We wouldn't be wearing them right now if it weren't for all of you!
Fans: They look amazing!
Fans: We love them!! They're so cute!!
Minori: Thank you so much! Again, we can't even begin to show our appreciation...
Minori: And I'm able to stand here today because... Even though I still have a long way to go as an idol, you've been willing to support me.
Yuina: Minori...
Minori: I know that I still need a lot of work, so it feels a little strange hearing you all cheer for me...
Minori: But each of your calls and cheers means so much to me... They really mean everything.
Minori: They're like raindrops that fall on my head and fill my heart with joy. Each one makes me want to try just that much harder!
Minori: So, once more... Thank you all very much!
Fans: Thank you too!!
Fans: *Sob* I'm so glad that I kept rooting for you, Minori!! I promise to be your fan forever!!
Minori: *Gasp* Thank you! I'll be looking forward to your continued support!
Minori: I don't know what to say... All your kind words have left me speechless.
Minori: And, um... I know I've been talking for a while now... But the person you see standing here today...
Minori: She wants to take everything you've given her and make this show as amazing as possible...!
Minori: So, uh... How's the show been?!
Fans: Amazing!
Yuina: Yeah... It's been really amazing...
Minori: Hehe. That's great to hear! Over the course of this show, I've been feeling so much of your energy...
Minori: This is what I've always wanted to do... It's been my dream to perform on stage and bring our hearts together.
Minori: Each and every one of you helped make that happen. So, to everyone in attendance...
Minori: To Airi and Shizuku, who helped prepare me to perform on this stage...
Minori: And to my hero... My role model forever... Haruka...
Minori: I appreciate everything you've all done for me! Thank you all so so so much!!
Haruka: Thank you for giving us such a wonderful speech, Minori...
Minori: I-It was? I'm not sure if what I said just now made any sense.
Airi: Hehe. Don't worry. Just take a look at everyone's faces.
Fans: That was awesome!!!
Fans: We love MMJ!!!
Minori: Thank you, everyone!
Haruka: The rest of us are well aware that Minori didn't have it easy at first since we all have experience being idols...
Haruka: But you kept persevering, Minori. As a result, you gave us an enormous amount of hope and encouragement.
Minori: Haruka...
Haruka: It's the reason why I'm so happy to be standing on this stage with you today. Because I know this solo show is your big moment.
Haruka: So, let's keep doing our best... Together!
Minori: Oh...
Minori: Yeah...
Minori: Thank you so much, Haruka! I finally made it this far.
Minori: Don't give up on your dreams, Minorinrin! Here's a bouquet of hope for you! Hello! I'm Minori Hanasato from MORE MORE JUMP!
Minori: I promise to do my absolute best moving forward, and I hope you'll be there to support me!
Fans: I'm so moved by just how much Minori's grown as an idol. I think I'm gonna cry...
Fans: Yeah, she's pretty great... It must've been so hard until now since the other members of MMJ are famous idols.
Fans: But Minori's different... She understands why idols are so great. It's like she's growing with us... It's hard not to root for her...
Yuina: ...
Yuina: (That's exactly right... Minori works super hard at everything. She gives you so much energy that there's no way you can't cheer for her.)
Yuina: (I'm so glad everyone else understands that too. But...)
Yuina: (I want more and more people to see just how amazing Minori really is...)
Airi: Now then...
Airi: It's time for our last song!
Shizuku: Get ready, everyone!
Haruka: This is our surprise to you! Let's keep raising the energy in this place!
Minori, Haruka, Shizuku & Airi: More and more and more!
Hasegawa: (My song... It's become the last song of this incredible show...)
Hasegawa: (So much happened while writing it too... I caused them so much trouble...)
Airi & Shizuku: ♪————
Minori & Haruka: ♪————!
Hasegawa: Thank goodness...
Len: <Hey, you two okay...?>
Miku: <*Sob* Our feelings started to synchronize after watching them all this time...>
Rin: <Yeah... This show... It's way too good...!!>
Luka: <Hehe. I know exactly how you feel... They've become such wonderful idols.>
MEIKO: <Yes, and they've certainly given me quite a bit of hope.>
MEIKO: <Also, I think Minori was spot on about how idols are able to both give and receive hope.>
KAITO: <I agree. Idols have a close relationship with their audience...>
KAITO: <So it's only natural for both parties to cheer for one another. It's really a wonderful thing.>
Rin: <I wanna see them grow even more as idols... I wanna see them really make it big...>
Miku: <Me too... And I'm sure they'll be able to spread hope to so many people down the road.>
Miku: <Thank you all so much for inviting us to see this incredible show...!>
